data.description: Don't miss this opportunity. single family home. move-in ready, Great Location Light, bright, and airy, updated 3-bedroom home located in the Trailwinds neighborhood of Fort Myers. A very central location close to shopping, dining, schools and more, lots of parking space Bring ALL the toys...work vehicles, boats, RV's, ATV's. Home has been well maintained and a lot of updates made. The kitchen comes with Brand new appliances, including washer and dryer, New Roof replaced in 2023, New water heater and gutters, large patio room for your kids to play also gives you the opportunity of enjoying tropical Florida weather and planting your favorites fruits and vegetables.
